&lt;p&gt;The Diamond Jubilee Maternity Unit births in excess of 5250 women a year. We are proud of our unit and are looking for a fail safe support officer to join our fail safe team to ensure that all samples that are taken and are disseminated to the clinical area appropriately. This role is also support the fail safe officers with monitoring of screening requirements as per NHS screening programmes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is for 15hrs per week, covering Monday-Friday (3hrs per day)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
